info.description:
Models
######

resnet-cifar10
##############

*ResNet classifier for CIFAR-10*

Operations
==========

train
^^^^^

*Train the ResNet model on CIFAR-10 data*

Flags
-----

**batch-size**
  *Number of images per batch*

**data-format**
  *Data format used by the model (channels_first or channels_last)*

**epochs**
  *Number of epochs to train*

**epochs-per-eval**
  *Number of epochs to run in between evaluations*

**resnet-size**
  *Size of the ResNet model to use*


resnet-imagenet
###############

*ResNet classifier for ImageNet*

Note, this model requires that the ImageNet dataset be available and prepared
as TFRrecords. Refer to https://git.io/vFQNF for instructions on preparing the
dataset.

Operations
==========

train
^^^^^

*Train the ResNet model on ImageNet data*

Flags
-----

**batch-size**
  *Number of images per batch*

**data-dir**
  *ImageNet data location*

**data-format**
  *Data format used by the model (channels_first or channels_last)*

**epochs**
  *Number of epochs to train*

**epochs-per-eval**
  *Number of epochs to run in between evaluations*

**resnet-size**
  *Size of the ResNet model to use (18, 34, 50, 101, 152, or 200)*


References
##########
